ast.value:
This is based on the minimalist Haskell "quicksort".

   Remark: this is *not* really quicksort since it doesn't partition the elements in-place

states.pp:
α : Type u_1,
lt : α → α → bool
⊢ qsort lt nil = nil

α : Type u_1,
lt : α → α → bool,
h : α,
t : list α
⊢ qsort lt (h :: t) =
    (λ (_a : list α × list α),
       _a.cases_on (λ (fst snd : list α), id_rhs (list α) (qsort lt snd ++ h :: qsort lt fst)))
      (partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t)

α : Type u_1,
lt : α → α → bool,
h : α,
t : list α
⊢ (λ (_x : list α × list α) (e : partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t = _x),
       prod.rec
         (λ (large small : list α) (e : partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t = (large, small)),
            qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) small ++ h :: qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) large)
         _x
         e)
      (partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t)
      _ =
    (λ (_a : list α × list α),
       _a.cases_on
         (λ (fst snd : list α),
            id_rhs (list α) (qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) snd ++ h :: qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) fst)))
      (partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t)

α : Type u_1,
lt : α → α → bool,
h : α,
t large small : list α,
e : partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t = (large, small)
⊢ (λ (_x : list α × list α) (e : partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t = _x),
       prod.rec
         (λ (large small : list α) (e : partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t = (large, small)),
            qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) small ++ h :: qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) large)
         _x
         e)
      (partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t)
      _ =
    (λ (_a : list α × list α),
       _a.cases_on
         (λ (fst snd : list α),
            id_rhs (list α) (qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) snd ++ h :: qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) fst)))
      (partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t)

α : Type u_1,
lt : α → α → bool,
h : α,
t large small : list α,
e : partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t = (large, small)
⊢ qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) small ++ h :: qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) large =
    prod.rec
      (λ (fst snd : list α),
         id_rhs (list α) (qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) snd ++ h :: qsort._proof_1.fix (qsort.F lt) fst))
      (partition (λ (x : α), lt h x = tt) t)
